parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the climate control panel knob can cause the driver to lose control of the heating and cooling system, leading to impaired visibility due to foggy windows, which can result in accidents or unsafe driving conditions.

the temperature control is stuck in one position
the air conditioning or heating does not function properly.

and uncertainty about the availability of parts.
